    "guides.verifyBody": "This is the stage buyers most often skip and most often regret. Before any money moves, confirm the project's registration on the HARERA portal yourself — not from a screenshot, from the portal — and read what the promoter has declared there. The registration record carries the promoter's own completion date, the sanctioned plans and any complaints filed. It is the one account of the project the developer did not write for you.",
