    "brabus.ethos.luxury.t": "Luxury",
    "brabus.ethos.luxury.d": "Bespoke interiors and premium finishes — Italian marble, branded fittings, materials chosen the way a marque chooses its own.",
    "brabus.ethos.performance.t": "Performance",
    "brabus.ethos.performance.d": "Systems engineered to perform: VRV climate control and smart-home integration, tuned to run quietly and precisely.",
    "brabus.ethos.exclusivity.t": "Exclusivity",
    "brabus.ethos.exclusivity.d": "An ultra-low-density plan and a limited collection — a villa-like home in a high-rise format, for the few.",
    "brabus.quoteA": "A residence should be",
    "brabus.quoteB": "engineered, not decorated.",
    "brabus.meaningKicker": "What a branded residence means",
    "brabus.meaning.designLanguage.t": "A design language, not a logo",
    "brabus.meaning.designLanguage.d": "The marque's ethos shapes proportion, material and detail — the residence is designed to its standard, not merely badged with its name.",
    "brabus.meaning.measure.t": "Finished to a marque's measure",
    "brabus.meaning.measure.d": "Italian marble, modular kitchens with branded fittings and premium hardware — specified rather than left to the buyer.",
    "brabus.meaning.perform.t": "Engineered to perform",
    "brabus.meaning.perform.d": "VRV air conditioning, smart-home integration and energy-efficient systems, so the building behaves as precisely as it looks.",
    "brabus.meaning.scarcity.t": "Scarcity by design",
    "brabus.meaning.scarcity.d": "Ultra-low density and a limited collection — the value of a branded residence rests on how few there are.",
